# Keep the repository limited to the extension's essential runtime files.
# Ignore everything by default, then allow-list the files needed to run it.
*

# Allow Git to traverse directories.
!*/

# Project metadata and docs.
!.gitignore
!README.md

# Firefox extension runtime files.
!manifest.json
!content.js
!popup.html
!popup.css
!popup.js
!icon-48.png
!icon-96.png

# Common local/generated files intentionally ignored by the default rule:
# .DS_Store
# .claude/
# ENV/
# *.zip
# helper scripts and generated assets
